1. *Bicikl* je moj omiljeni prevoz (The bicycle is my favorite means of transportation).
2. Kupio sam novi *bicikl* u prodavnici sportke opreme (I bought a new bicycle at the sports equipment store).
3. Nisam vozio *bicikl* od detinjstva (I haven't ridden a bicycle since childhood).
4. *Biciklom* idem do posla svaki dan (I go to work by bicycle every day).
5. *Bicikl* je bio parkiran ispred zgrade (The bicycle was parked in front of the building).
6. Održavam svoj *bicikl* redovno (I maintain my bicycle regularly).
7. Prešao sam veliku udaljenost *biciklom* (I covered a long distance by bicycle).
8. *Bicikl* mi je ukraden u centru grada (My bicycle was stolen in the city center).
9. *Bicikl* je jednostavan za korišćenje (The bicycle is easy to use).
10. Učim svoje dete da vozi *bicikl* (I am teaching my child to ride a bicycle).